Text: Re Board approvalHi Jeff This is so very exciting I will write you an official thank you from Temple but I also wanted to fly you an email again I look forward to your Bulletin Article and as a mother of Youth Groupers I would love it when you are in town some time next year youth group is kind of down for the summer now to have you come and speak to the kids if you would All of us exTYGers have a powerful message and yours will certainly reach these kids Thank you again Warm regards Julie Benson
